OL,3,CMan charged with rape and murder after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman in her 80s
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith rape and murder following the
OL,8,Fdeath of a woman in her 80s in Helston.
OL,10,FEdward Holden, of Alexandra Place,
OL,11,FPenzance, will appear before Truro
OL,12,FMagistrates Court on Monday 1 June.
OL,14,FDevon and Cornwall Police say the
OL,15,Fcharge is in connection with an
OL,16,Fincident in the Ashton area, which was
OL,17,Freported to them on Friday 29 May.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
