OL,3,CMan charged with rape and murder after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman in her 80s
OL,6,FIn a statement, the force said: "We
OL,7,Frecognise that an incident such as
OL,8,Fthis will cause worry amongst our
OL,9,Fcommunities.
OL,11,F"We would specifically request that
OL,12,Fany social media commentary is
OL,13,Favoided, and we ask for your support
OL,14,Fas we further our investigations."
